  "StockRole": "Scout",
  "YangsThoughts": "Clan Diamond Shark built this at the turn of the 32nd century and the engine alone takes up 40% of the total mass. Most of the ones produced ended up with wealthy private buyers using them for illegal street racing in the Periphery rather than actual military service. A former pirate named Ryan Reynolds bought one, won a bunch of races, then hit a canyon wall at nearly 400 kph on Tincalunas in 3142. Finding one of these intact and operational is almost unbelievable.",
